llm_res.rule: Returns the total token supply. function totalSupply() public view returns (uint256)

Transfers _value amount of tokens from address _from to address _to, and MUST fire the Transfer event. The function SHOULD throw if the message caller’s account balance does not have enough tokens to spend. Note Transfers of 0 values MUST be treated as normal transfers and fire the Transfer event. function transferFrom(address _from, address _to, uint256 _value) public returns (bool success)
